Host godzilla occult magic wizard
    User harper
    LogLevel VERBOSE

    ControlMaster auto
    ControlPersist 10m
    ControlPath ~/.ssh/cm-%r@%h:%p

    ForwardAgent yes
    Compression yes
    PreferredAuthentications publickey
    VerifyHostKeyDNS yes
    PasswordAuthentication yes


